nFromWeb?topicID=107.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What class do you Fear the most in PvP?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Melees are laughable if trying to PK someone<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>this does not hold true for rogues. i can PK int casters just fine... alone.. or with friends. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/umordier.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mordier</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/19/01 8:03:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=107.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What class do you Fear the most in PvP?</span><hr size=1> Aye.  The fact that they made druids "a class to fear" in pvp is *almost* enough to make me not want to play the game.  There's nothing worse than losing to a druid.<br><br>Personally, I fear the green skull. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/umordier.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mordier</A> at: 2/20/01 6:47:44 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/uceescritdabossalini.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ceescrit da Bossalini</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/20/01 8:35:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=107.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What class do you Fear the most in PvP?</span><hr size=1> Heh, and